.TH mate-mouse-properties 1 "2014\-05\-02" "MATE"
.SH NAME
\fBmate-mouse-properties \fP- configure MATE mouse preferences
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B mate-mouse-properties
.RI [--get-legacy]
.SH DESCRIPTION
This executable is part of the package 'mate\-control\-center': The MATE Control Center.
.PP
The MATE  mouse  preference  tool  enables you to configure your mouse for right-hand or
left-hand use. It is also used to specify the speed and sensitivity of mouse movement
and mouse button press events.
.SH OPTIONS
The following options are supported:
.TP
.B
\fB--get-legacy\fP
Retrieve and store legacy settings
.PP
This program also accepts the standard MATE and GTK options.
